    "updated_at": "2018-09-24T17:02:29Z",
    "body": "Triage: this is a pain point that we still feel today, especially on Windows. That being said, keeping an issue open to track it isn't really helping; we may or may not change rustdoc to fix this, or a successor to rustdoc might. I don't think this issue is very useful for tracking that, so I'm going to give it a close. Thanks!",
